 pot.  </li><li><a href="https://artmuseum.indiana.edu/visit/your-visit.ht
 ml">Where to find us\, where to park\, accessibility\, and museum guideli
 nes</a>.  </li><li>This workshop is recommended for ages 12 and up. Anyon
 e under 18\, who is not an IU student\, must be accompanied by an adult. 
  </li></ul><h3><strong>When You Arrive</strong></h3><ul><li><strong>Check
  in with Guest Services at the information desk on the first floor\, even
