SUMMARY:Summer Art Camp: Creating with Nature
DESCRIPTION:Each day of the nature-inspired week includes hands-on projec
 ts like painting\, printmaking\, sculpture\, and mixed media\, along with
  fun outdoor exploration (weatherpermitting). By the end of the week\, st
 udents will have a collection of artwork celebrating the beauty and inspi
 ration of the natural world.  Art lessons and activities are thoughtfully
  designed and led by our licensed art educator.  Drop-off and pick-up inf
 ormation will be shared via email after registration.12-3 pm Monday - Fri
 day.
