 ith</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW86518705 BCX0">different materia
 ls</span><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW86518705 BCX0">\, and develop the
 ir own artistic style. By the end of the week\, teens will leave with a c
 ollection of meaningful artwork and fresh inspiration.</span></p><p data-
 start="0" data-end="90">  Art lessons and activities are thoughtfully des
 igned and led by our licensed art educator.</p><p data-start="92" data-en
 d="169" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">  Drop-off and pick-up 
 information\, as well as teen driver information\, will be shared via ema
 il after registration.</p><p data-start="92" data-end="169" data-is-last-
 node="" data-is-only-node=""><span class="NormalTextRun SCXW75914810 BCX0
 ">12-3 pm Monday - Friday.</span></p>
